    "body": "IMO the best solution would be be to have per-mod settings for everything except player name and graphics configuration, but then share settings (remembering unknown settings, as per this ticket) across different versions of the same mod.\r\n\r\nI don't consider it worthwhile to support the use case of having two different versions of the same mod running at the same time."
